cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically using event-driven cameras for visual tracking on a moving robot. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and machine learning, which suggests the categories cs.RO (Robotics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as likely sub-categories.
